Usage: send-text [message...] [options]

Options include:
  --help,-h      prints this help
  --from,-f      sender-of-text defaults to hostname
  --to,-t        cell phone number of receiver [i.e. 4512345678]
  --key,-k       your nexmo api key
  --secret,-s    your nexmo api secret
  --defaults,-d  save the current passed options as defaults

